### Arabic

خُذِ ٱلْعَفْوَ وَأْمُرْ بِٱلْعُرْفِ وَأَعْرِضْ عَنِ ٱلْجَـٰهِلِينَ

### English

Be gracious, enjoin what is right, and turn away from those who act ignorantly.